      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just left the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, always garage-kept, and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, you\u2019ve found it. Feel free to reach out with any questions, I'd love to show it to you!",
